<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="1Sep1928"><font color="red">1 September 1928</font> <i>Letters III</i> (to Benjamin Conner): (dictated) I have been ill with my eyes the last three weeks &hellip; I was much relieved to receive the copies of parts 10 and 11 of Work in Progress and to know that the copyright of this portion of the book also has been properly taken out in my name in the United States. I hope you received for this purpose also copies of Transition No 13 </div>
